{
  "stem": "12494.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went home, which was a walk of about 15, 20 minutes-- I forgot whether I walked or whether I took to the streetcar-- and went out on Parliament Square.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was quite obvious that Budapest was occupied because [INAUDIBLE] there were German sentries in front of all the public buildings in Parliament Square.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I went back to our house, the house where our flat was, we occupied the-- what you would call in this country, the third floor, we call it the second floor-- of the building.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's where our flat was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And found my mother and my brother, and want to get in touch with my father.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father's headquarters was-- we were in Battery Street 4, his headquarters was in Battery Street 5.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was the headquarters of his company.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it was Sunday, and he wouldn't take the phone, and there wasn't anybody else in.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so I couldn't get to him, so I ran over to 5, and rang the bell in the hope that he would answer.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But he didn't answer.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went back home, and we were all quite desperate.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We knew that something important was going on, and that Papa was locked in his office.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we couldn't get to him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I even tried to-- I-- I threw stones, little pebbles-- at his window-- the first floor.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But there was no reaction.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so we were waiting, and-- and we were quite upset.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then arrived the-- the Polish general-- forgot his name, I think it was [NON-ENGLISH], [?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Masovske, Mervske, something-- Masovske ?].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he wanted to talk to my father, and my father wasn't there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And-- so we were all waiting.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
